# Input

```svelte
{#each items as item}
  <div>{item}</div>
{:else}
  <div>No items found</div>
{/each}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#each items as item}
	<div>{item}</div>
{:else}
	<div>No items found</div>
{/each}

```
